                      &trans            &trans     &kp UP        &trans             &kp LBRC            &kp RBRC  &trans          &kp COLON      &trans        &trans
                      &kp LG(LEFT_ALT)  &kp LEFT   &kp DOWN      &kp RIGHT          &kp LBKT            &kp RBKT  &kp MINUS       &kp PLUS       &kp ASTERISK  &kp SLASH
&kp C_AL_SCREENSAVER  &trans            &kp GRAVE  &kp SQT       &kp DOUBLE_QUOTES  &kp LPAR            &kp RPAR  &kp UNDERSCORE  &kp SEMICOLON  &kp TILDE     &kp BACKSLASH  &trans
                                                   &kp LEFT_ALT  &kp LCTRL          &kp LEFT_COMMAND    &trans    &trans          &trans
            >;
